A VERY SAD AND TWISTED TURN OF EVENTS, ALAN.
<P>
THAT TOW TRUCK DRIVER WAS STUCK WITH A HYPODERMIC NEEDLE *FILLED* WITH BLOOD AND DRUGS WHILE TOWING THAT CAR YESTERDAY.
<P>
THIS, AFTER BEING CALLED OUT BY A SANTA CRUZ COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPUTY. WHO HAD A HARROWING EXPERIENCE OF HIS OWN.
<P>

