<A NAME=131gilroy cat fire>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>gilroy cat fire</H3><BR>
A CAT IN GILROY IS TONIGHT BEING CREDITED WITH SAVING ITS OWNERS LIFE.
<P>
HELEN LETTERMAN WAS FAST ASLEEP LAST NIGHT. WHEN HER CLOTHES DRYER SPARKED A FIRE.
<P>
THERE WERE NO SMOKE ALARMS IN THE HOUSE. AND HELEN DIDN'T WAKE UP UNTIL ONE OF HER CATS JUMPED ON HER FACE.
<P>
SHE GRABBED HER FELINE HERO. AND BOTH SCRAMBLED TO SAFETY.
<P>
THE FIRE WAS CONTAINED IN THE LAUNDRY ROOM. BUT SEVERAL OTHER CATS WERE KILLED IN THE FIRE.
<P>

